{"tid":2390542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國內政部常秘：BNO簽證是英國對香港人的歷史和道德承諾","createTime":"2021-02-01T15:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T15:16:55.000Z","uid":70063,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4318768d2b94f502e0bf4f26bd3623cd71b42469","tid":2390542,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T15:14:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/MatthewRycroft1/status/1355104603948396545\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMatthewRycroft1%2Fstatus%2F1355104603948396545&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQlzC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=de96b66e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMatthewRycroft1%2Fstatus%2F1355104603948396545&h=fba6d384\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/MatthewRycroft1/status/1355104603948396545</a><br />\n<br />\n正當中共外交部表示不再承認BNO為旅行證件之際，負責BNO事宜的英國內政部常秘Matthew Rycroft表示，英國周日開放BNO簽證服務，這是英國對香港人的歷史及道德義務，尤其是當香港人的自由及權利受到限制的時候。<br />\n<br />\n他又感謝內政部公務員團隊近月一直為BNO事宜所作的努力。的而且確，英方自去年起，內政部職員須處理大量有關BNO的查詢，相信隨着正式接受網上申請，之後會忙到一頭煙。<br />\n<br />\n為了樹立香港人的良好形象，值得大家去多謝對方，感謝公務員為香港所作的付出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ukhomeoffice/status/1355084463282204674\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fukhomeoffice%2Fstatus%2F1355084463282204674&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQlzC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=355e97d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fukhomeoffice%2Fstatus%2F1355084463282204674&h=4e20e4d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ukhomeoffice/status/1355084463282204674</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HKinternationalfront/409\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKinternationalfront%2F409&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQlzC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=30216ff9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKinternationalfront/409</a>"},{"pid":"04629387c8f5cf1c11faa5f0ccfad95530397d7b","tid":2390542,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T15:15:46.000Z","msg":"大英祖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"401c011ef379f7c91ee6fc26088dada8b49cd9ad","tid":2390542,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T15:15:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80dccc11907f8afec746301af4040bece3f54793","tid":2390542,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T15:16:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/83bFcfg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F83bFcfg.jpg&h=4291a07f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}